<p>
  Each file is independently versioned, independently auditable, and independently updateable. The soul doesn't change when you add a new tool to the body. The conscience doesn't soften when the shadow detects sycophancy. The ego mediates conflicts between layers at runtime — just like the Freudian ego mediates between id, superego, and reality.
</p>

